    <item>
      <title>短期国库券的枯竭可能会导致美联储紧缩资产负债表的结局变得混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/a-drought-of-treasury-bills-risks-muddying-the-end-of-fed-s-qt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年因发行大量国债而苦苦挣扎的国债投资者现在正准备面对相反的挑战：销售回落导致他们手头有大量现金，需要在其他地方使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/a-drought-of-treasury-bills-risks-muddying-the-end-of-fed-s-qt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可口可乐提高价格，盈利超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/consumer-staples-mcdonald-s-and-coke-report-earnings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国增长放缓和中东战争，麦当劳公布的盈利未达到预期。可口可乐提高了价格，第一季度盈利超出了华尔街的预期。凯蒂·格雷菲尔德报道。 （更正标题以删除消费必需品参考。）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/consumer-staples-mcdonald-s-and-coke-report-earnings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗格夫表示市场将挫败美联储面临的任何政治压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/rogoff-says-markets-would-upend-political-bashing-of-the-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学经济学教授肯尼思·罗格夫表示，金融市场将有效限制美国总统迫使美联储放松货币政策的任何举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/rogoff-says-markets-would-upend-political-bashing-of-the-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦当劳可能不会很快反弹：BTIG 的萨利赫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/mcdonald-s-might-not-rebound-anytime-soon-btig-s-saleh-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BTIG 餐厅董事总经理彼得·萨利赫 (Peter Saleh) 表示，麦当劳的价值信息不会“很快扭转局面”。他在彭博电视上与凯蒂·格雷菲尔德进行了交谈。麦当劳的可比销售额增长率为 1.9%，低于彭博社调查的分析师预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/mcdonald-s-might-not-rebound-anytime-soon-btig-s-saleh-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:06:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ADM 股价下跌，首席执行官表示已从繁荣时期过渡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/adm-s-profit-drops-less-than-expected-on-higher-volumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司(Archer-Daniels-Midland Co.)的股价下跌，因为这家农业综合企业巨头警告称，尽管季度收益超出预期，但今年剩余时间利润率将面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/adm-s-profit-drops-less-than-expected-on-higher-volumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:28:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场看到美联储在美国利率会议上发表鹰派言论，金价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/gold-set-to-gain-for-third-straight-month-ahead-of-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价下滑——收窄了连续第三个月的涨幅——投资者焦点转向本周的美联储会议，预计政策制定者将在利率问题上采取强硬态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/gold-set-to-gain-for-third-straight-month-ahead-of-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
